## Loading Fixtures

```ruby
# Load all fixtures (default)
class ArticleTest < ActiveSupport::TestCase
  fixtures :all
end

# Load specific fixtures
class ArticleTest < ActiveSupport::TestCase
  fixtures :articles, :users
end

# Access fixtures
test "user has articles" do
  user = users(:john)
  assert user.articles.any?
end
```

